rows.label: qst103302_msg001
rows.name: 主人がお世話になってます(仮)

rows.label: qst103302_msg101
rows.name: よろしくお願いします(仮)

rows.label: qst103302_msg201
rows.name: 殺人事件が起きたから現場まで来て(仮)

rows.label: qst103302_msg0001
rows.name:
My master considers me part of
his family. He is truly a kind soul.

rows.label: qst103302_msg0101
rows.name:
I am sorry, but there was
an incident and my master
was urgently summoned.

rows.label: qst103302_msg0102
rows.name: Apparently there has been a murder.

rows.label: qst103302_msg0103
rows.name:
The crime scene is the Shamayim Hot
Springs. Do you want to try looking
for him there?

rows.label: qst103302_msg0104
rows.name:
Very well, then.
I will meet you there.
